   <td colspan="4" class="content">
    <pre>Thoughts:

* I would suggest, rather than shipping a new fixture, modifying the Person
object in your test_get_full_name_and_username_for_user_with_no_full_name()
function.

* for "get_absolute_url()" I would suggest you either use plain old string
addition (rather than "".join()), or use the urlparse module to assemble a URL.
But string addition would be fine.

* The link you generate in landing_page_for_logged_in_users.html -- inside the
&lt;a href=""&gt; -- I'd prefer that be surrounded with quotation marks. That's
something I'll add on.

Otherwise, that looks good. Good enough to ship! Feel free to fix these things I
suggested, or not, I guess. (-:

<a href="https://openhatch.org/+feeds/activity/">https://openhatch.org/+feeds/activity/</a> !!!!</pre>
