    <pre>re: feed templates:

You should use {% reverse %} in landing_page_for_logged_in_users.html

re: feed implementation:

You should write a test for get_full_name_and_username.

Also, Answer.get_question_text is pretty strange -- you're doing "in"
comparisons with strings. Are you sure that's right?

You calculate "project_string" repeatedly in the function.

You should also use the Django URL helper functions in Answer.get_absolute_url.

I would probably just fix some of this up, but I really have to go to sleep! So
I think it'll miss the milestone )-:</pre>
